Ici, une paire de 7.

257
00:32:48,782 --> 00:32:50,441
Là, rien.

258
00:32:50,702 --> 00:32:53,158
Un bel as !

259
00:32:53,774 --> 00:32:54,668
Je relance.

260
00:32:58,062 --> 00:32:59,524
Je vois.

261
00:33:10,127 --> 00:33:10,989
Un dollar.

262
